data.eml:eml: A new cave Sinella species from South China (Collembola: Entomobryidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Zhang, Feng, Deharveng, Louis (2009): A new cave Sinella species from South China (Collembola: Entomobryidae). Zootaxa 2009: 35-40, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.185768
